data.description: Welcome to your Dream home in the beautiful city of Phelan.  This magnificent 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a large family room is a dream come true.  As you approach this charming home you will be captivated by so many surrounding shade trees.    The property has many fruit trees and shade trees.  Zoned for some animals and horses, home offers ample space for your 4 footed critters to roam. The front porch and rear porch offer shade for the barbecues on hot summer days and beautiful sunsets.  The 3 bedrooms are spacious, the Master bedroom offers 2 showers, First with a sitting area,and two shower heads, for those with limited movement, and the other shower a stand-up, the second bathroom offers a shower and soaking tub. The Kitchen offers ample counter space with updated dishwasher and stove.  Separate indoor laundry room, leads to the back yard.  The family room is large and has a wood burning fireplace that can be used as a stove and can easily be converted to a 4th bedroom.  Home also offers a small additional living quarters.  Home is completely wired with Security system as well as a 6 foot fence with automatic opener.  Garage also has a automatic door. Come take a look at this 2.5 acre home, m ake an appointment today.
